		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Of course you can read from OAM! How else could I have reverse-engineered the PPU's sprite fetch behaviour?
<br />
<br />The only caveat is that reading $2004 does <strong>not</strong> increment the address pointer ($2003) - only writing does that.

		

